    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC describes the Exterior Gateway Protocol used to connect Stub Gateways to an Autonomous System of core Gateways.  This document specifies the working protocol, and defines an ARPA official protocol.  All implementers of Gateways should carefully review this document.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
